It is expected that theartisanal fleet will be fully registered through physical registration by the 4th year of the project. In the meanwhile and as awayto continue monitoring the fishing capacity, census should be carried out until the entire fleet is registered. | Due Date:30-Nov-2016

Finance Agreement :Mauritania: allocation of fishing rights in the octopus industry. | Description :Mauritania: The allocation offishing rights in the octopus industry is equitable, in a manner satisfactory to the Association.
